snippet.title: JumpStart Dino Adventure Field Trip Game Boy Color Playthrough
snippet.description:
Yeah, that's right. A JumpStart game on a Nintendo console. Normally I would use an emulator, but I had to use my GameCube with the Game Boy Player using an original physical copy of the game to record this since the available ROM for it had problems. In this game, Frankie take a trip to the dinosaur world using Hopsalot and CJ's time machine, and then Frankie goes on his quest to find the pterodactyl's lost eggs, and even find the time machine since it got stolen by a dino who mistook it for an egg.

There was also JumpStart Wildlife Safari Field Trip for the PlayStation, the console counterpart to this game, and there were also JumpStart games for the Nintendo Wii, and even one for the Nintendo DS.
